Harmony Gold Says Production Fell by 2% to 316,909 Ounce in Third Quarter

-- B y   C a r l i   L o u r e n s
-- 
2011-05-05T05:59:38Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-05-05/harmony-gold-says-production-fell-by-2-to-316-909-ounce-in-third-quarter.html
Harmony Gold Mining Co. said
production in the three months to March 31 fell 2 percent to
316,909 ounces from the previous quarter.  Harmony commented in a statement published on its website
today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
